  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "n1",
      "type": "segment",
      "title": "火车闲聊",
      "next": "n2"
    },
    {
      "id": "n2",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "station_night.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "叙利亚，冬季，清晨五点钟。阿勒颇站台旁停着托罗斯快车，寒冷刺骨。",
      "next": "n3"
    },
    {
      "id": "n3",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "station_night.png",
      "speaker": "lieutenant",
      "text": "今天是星期日，明天，星期一晚上，您就到斯坦布尔了。",
      "next": "n4"
    },
    {
      "id": "n4",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "station_night.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "是啊。我从没去过斯坦布尔，错过了会很遗憾——是的。",
      "next": "n5"
    },
    {
      "id": "n5",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "station_night.png",
      "speaker": "lieutenant",
      "text": "我想，您打算在那儿待几天吧？",
      "next": "n6"
    },
    {
      "id": "n6",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "station_night.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "没错。我从没去过斯坦布尔，错过了会很遗憾——是的。没有负担——我会在那儿游览几天。",
      "next": "n7"
    },
    {
      "id": "n7",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "station_night.png",
      "speaker": "lieutenant",
      "text": "圣索菲，很漂亮。",
      "next": "n8"
    },
    {
      "id": "n8",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "玛丽·德贝纳姆从卧铺车厢的窗帘缝隙向外看。她睡眠不足，心情烦躁。",
      "next": "n9"
    },
    {
      "id": "n9",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window.png",
      "speaker": "debenham",
      "text": "（心想）这一定是阿勒颇。当然没什么好看的……",
      "next": "n10"
    },
    {
      "id": "n10",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "她看到窗外有两个男人在交谈——一个是法国军官，另一个是留着夸张小胡子的矮个子。",
      "next": "n11"
    },
    {
      "id": "n11",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_corridor.png",
      "speaker": "conductor",
      "text": "请上车，先生。火车就要开了。",
      "next": "n12"
    },
    {
      "id": "n12",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_corridor.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "（装出不舍的样子上了火车）",
      "next": "n13"
    },
    {
      "id": "n13",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_corridor.png",
      "speaker": "lieutenant",
      "text": "（敬礼）一路顺风！",
      "next": "n14"
    },
    {
      "id": "n14",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_corridor.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "（嘟囔）可算结束了！",
      "next": "n15"
    },
    {
      "id": "n15",
      "type": "choice",
      "bg": "train_corridor.png",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "c1",
          "text": "继续默默观察",
          "next": "segment_observation_start"
        },
        {
          "id": "c2",
          "text": "主动打招呼",
          "next": "segment_observation_start"
        },
        {
          "id": "c3",
          "text": "询问列车员关于她的事",
          "next": "segment_observation_start"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "segment_observation_start",
      "type": "segment",
      "title": "观察上校与小姐的对话",
      "next": "n16"
    },
    {
      "id": "n16",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_compartment.png",
      "speaker": "conductor",
      "text": "先生的小旅行袋，我放这儿了。",
      "next": "n17"
    },
    {
      "id": "n17",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_compartment.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "（递过小费）谢谢。",
      "next": "n18"
    },
    {
      "id": "n18",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_compartment.png",
      "speaker": "conductor",
      "text": "谢谢，先生。我看旅行的人不太多呢。",
      "next": "n19"
    },
    {
      "id": "n19",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_compartment.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "没几个吗？",
      "next": "n20"
    },
    {
      "id": "n20",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_compartment.png",
      "speaker": "conductor",
      "text": "除了您，只有两位旅客——都是英国人。来自印度的上校和从巴格达来的年轻的英国小姐。",
      "next": "n21"
    },
    {
      "id": "n21",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_compartment_night.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "清晨五点钟搭乘火车是个尴尬的时刻。还有两个小时才会天亮，考虑到晚上睡眠不足，并且刚刚成功地完成了一个棘手的任务，波洛先生蜷在角落里睡着了。",
      "next": "n22"
    },
    {
      "id": "n22",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car_morning.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "醒来时已经是九点半，他冲进餐车，想喝杯热咖啡。",
      "next": "n23"
    },
    {
      "id": "n23",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car_morning.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "此时那里只有一个旅客，很明显是列车员说的那位年轻的英国小姐。她身材修长苗条，黑色的头发，二十八岁上下。从她吃早饭以及让服务员添加咖啡的冷静样子来看，想必是个见多识广、经常旅行的人。她一身暗色的旅行装束，料子轻薄，很适合车上闷热的空气。",
      "next": "n24"
    },
    {
      "id": "n24",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car_morning.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "（心想）赫尔克里·波洛先生无事可做，为了打发时间，就装作若无其事地观察起她来。",
      "next": "n25"
    },
    {
      "id": "n25",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car_morning.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "（继续观察）她是在那种无论在哪都能照顾好自己的年轻女人，沉着能干。我尤其喜欢她那极为端正的五官和细致白皙的皮肤，也喜欢她那顺滑整洁的黑发，还有她那双冷淡的灰色眼睛。不过，她看起来太干练了，不是我心目的'美女'。",
      "next": "n26"
    },
    {
      "id": "n26",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car_morning.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "没过多久，另一个人走进了餐车。这是个四五十岁的高个子男人，身形偏瘦，棕色皮肤，两鬓略有些斑白。",
      "next": "n27"
    },
    {
      "id": "n27",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car_morning.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "（自言自语）印度来的上校。",
      "next": "n28"
    },
    {
      "id": "n28",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car_morning.png",
      "speaker": "arbuthnot",
      "text": "（微微鞠了一躬）早上好，德贝纳姆小姐。",
      "next": "n29"
    },
    {
      "id": "n29",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car_morning.png",
      "speaker": "debenham",
      "text": "早上好，阿巴思诺特上校。",
      "next": "n30"
    },
    {
      "id": "n30",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car_morning.png",
      "speaker": "arbuthnot",
      "text": "（站住了，一只手搭在她对面的椅子上）你介意吗？",
      "next": "n31"
    },
    {
      "id": "n31",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car_morning.png",
      "speaker": "debenham",
      "text": "当然不。请坐。",
      "next": "n32"
    },
    {
      "id": "n32",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car_morning.png",
      "speaker": "arbuthnot",
      "text": "呃，你知道，早饭可不是聊天的好时间。",
      "next": "n33"
    },
    {
      "id": "n33",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car_morning.png",
      "speaker": "debenham",
      "text": "正合我意。不过我不会咬人的。",
      "next": "n34"
    },
    {
      "id": "n34",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car_morning.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "上校坐了下来。",
      "next": "n35"
    },
    {
      "id": "n35",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car_morning.png",
      "speaker": "arbuthnot",
      "text": "（专横地命令道）服务员！",
      "next": "n36"
    },
    {
      "id": "n36",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car_morning.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "他点了鸡蛋和咖啡。他的视线在赫尔克里·波洛身上短暂地停顿了片刻，又毫不在意地移开了。",
      "next": "n37"
    },
    {
      "id": "n37",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car_morning.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "（心想）波洛明白这个英国人的想法，知道他准会这么自言自语：'只不过是个该死的外国佬。'",
      "next": "n38"
    },
    {
      "id": "n38",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car_morning.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "不愧是这个民族的，两个英国人并没有闲聊，只是简单地说了两句，女子就起身回自己的车厢了。",
      "next": "n39"
    },
    {
      "id": "n39",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car_day.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "午饭时，那两个人又坐在了同一张桌子旁边，仍然无视第三个旅客。他们的谈话比早饭时活跃了一些。阿巴思诺特上校说到了旁遮普，还间或询问了对方几个关于巴格达的问题。很明显，她在那儿当过家庭教师。谈话中他们发现了几个彼此共同的朋友，这立刻使二人友好起来，不再那么拘束了。他们提到了一个叫老汤米的人，还有一个老雷吉。",
      "next": "n40"
    },
    {
      "id": "n40",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car_day.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "上校问她是直接去英国还是在斯坦布尔下车。",
      "next": "n41"
    },
    {
      "id": "n41",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car_day.png",
      "speaker": "debenham",
      "text": "我直接去英国。",
      "next": "n42"
    },
    {
      "id": "n42",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car_day.png",
      "speaker": "arbuthnot",
      "text": "那岂不是很遗憾？",
      "next": "n43"
    },
    {
      "id": "n43",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car_day.png",
      "speaker": "debenham",
      "text": "两年前我也坐过这趟车，那时候在斯坦布尔度过了三天。",
      "next": "n44"
    },
    {
      "id": "n44",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car_day.png",
      "speaker": "arbuthnot",
      "text": "（略显笨拙地欠了欠身，脸色有点发红）哦，我明白了，我得说很高兴你直接去英国，因为我也是。",
      "next": "n45"
    },
    {
      "id": "n45",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car_day.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "（饶有兴致地想）我们的上校很容易动感情啊。这趟火车跟在海上航行一样危险！",
      "next": "n46"
    },
    {
      "id": "n46",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car_day.png",
      "speaker": "debenham",
      "text": "（淡然）那很不错。",
      "next": "n47"
    },
    {
      "id": "n47",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car_day.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "她的态度有些克制。波洛注意到上校陪她回了她的车厢。",
      "next": "n48"
    },
    {
      "id": "n48",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "mountain_scenery.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "后来，他们穿行在托罗斯壮丽的景色之中，两人肩并肩地站在过道上，俯瞰奇里乞亚门时，女子忽然叹了口气。波洛正站在他们旁边，听到她低声说道：",
      "next": "n49"
    },
    {
      "id": "n49",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "mountain_scenery.png",
      "speaker": "debenham",
      "text": "真美啊，我希望——我希望——",
      "next": "n50"
    },
    {
      "id": "n50",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "mountain_scenery.png",
      "speaker": "arbuthnot",
      "text": "什么？",
      "next": "n51"
    },
    {
      "id": "n51",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "mountain_scenery.png",
      "speaker": "debenham",
      "text": "我希望自己能欣赏它！",
      "next": "n52"
    },
    {
      "id": "n52",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "mountain_scenery.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "阿巴思诺特没有应答。他下巴的那条方形线条似乎更加严峻、冷酷了。",
      "next": "n53"
    },
    {
      "id": "n53",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "mountain_scenery.png",
      "speaker": "arbuthnot",
      "text": "希望上帝让你摆脱这一切。",
      "next": "n54"
    },
    {
      "id": "n54",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "mountain_scenery.png",
      "speaker": "debenham",
      "text": "嘘，请别说了。",
      "next": "n55"
    },
    {
      "id": "n55",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "mountain_scenery.png",
      "speaker": "arbuthnot",
      "text": "（有点气恼地向波洛这边扫了一眼）哦，好吧。不过我不喜欢你当家庭教师这个想法——对那些专横的妈妈和她们讨厌的小鬼唯命是从。",
      "next": "n56"
    },
    {
      "id": "n56",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "mountain_scenery.png",
      "speaker": "debenham",
      "text": "（笑了，声音有些失控）不，你不能这么想。家庭教师'饱受压迫'，是个已经被推翻了的传说。那些父母还怕被我欺负呢。",
      "next": "n57"
    },
    {
      "id": "n57",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "mountain_scenery.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "两人没再说话。也许阿巴思诺特对自己的感情爆发感到羞愧。",
      "next": "n58"
    },
    {
      "id": "n58",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "mountain_scenery.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "（沉思着自言自语）我在这儿看到了一幕奇怪的小喜剧。",
      "next": "n59"
    },
    {
      "id": "n59",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "mountain_scenery.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "他以后会记起这个想法的。",
      "next": "n60"
    },
    {
      "id": "n60",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "station_night_snow.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "那晚大约十一点半的时候，他们抵达科尼亚，那两个英国旅客下车伸展四肢，在布满积雪的站台上走来走去。",
      "next": "n61"
    },
    {
      "id": "n61",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "station_night_snow.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "波洛先生乐于透过玻璃窗观察车站上拥挤的情形。然而大约十分钟后，他觉得呼吸一下新鲜空气兴许不是件坏事，于是他仔细地准备了一番，用好几件大衣把自己裹严，围上围巾，又在整洁的靴子外面套上胶套鞋。穿戴完毕，他小心翼翼地走到站台上，一路向车头走去。",
      "next": "n62"
    },
    {
      "id": "n62",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "station_night_snow.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "一阵声音让他认出了站在货车厢阴影中的两个模糊的人影。阿巴思诺特正在说着：",
      "next": "n63"
    },
    {
      "id": "n63",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "station_night_snow.png",
      "speaker": "arbuthnot",
      "text": "玛丽——",
      "next": "n64"
    },
    {
      "id": "n64",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "station_night_snow.png",
      "speaker": "debenham",
      "text": "（打断了他）不是现在，不是现在。等一切都结束了，等事情过去了，再——",
      "next": "n65"
    },
    {
      "id": "n65",
      "type": "choice",
      "bg": "station_night_snow.png",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "c1",
          "text": "继续偷听",
          "next": "segment_train_stop_start"
        },
        {
          "id": "c2",
          "text": "故意发出声音提醒他们",
          "next": "segment_train_stop_start"
        },
        {
          "id": "c3",
          "text": "立即离开",
          "next": "segment_train_stop_start"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "segment_train_stop_start",
      "type": "segment",
      "title": "火车停车",
      "next": "n66"
    },
    {
      "id": "n66",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "station_night_snow.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "波洛先生小心地转身走开了，暗自纳闷……他差点没听出来德贝纳姆小姐那冷淡而干练的声音……",
      "next": "n67"
    },
    {
      "id": "n67",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "station_night_snow.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "（自言自语）奇怪。",
      "next": "n68"
    },
    {
      "id": "n68",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_corridor_day.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "第二天，不知道他们是否发生过口角，两人没怎么说话。他感觉那位姑娘心事重重的，眼睛周围也有了青晕。",
      "next": "n69"
    },
    {
      "id": "n69",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_stopped_day.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "大约下午两点半时，火车忽然停了。大家都把脑袋探出窗外，几个人聚在轨道旁，看着餐车下方，还指指点点的。",
      "next": "n70"
    },
    {
      "id": "n70",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_stopped_day.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "波洛也探出头，询问匆匆经过的列车员。那人回答完，波洛缩回脑袋，转过身，差点撞到站在他身后的玛丽·德贝纳姆小姐。",
      "next": "n71"
    },
    {
      "id": "n71",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_stopped_day.png",
      "speaker": "debenham",
      "text": "（急促地用法语问道）怎么了？为什么停车了？",
      "next": "n72"
    },
    {
      "id": "n72",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_stopped_day.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "没事，小姐，餐车下面有什么东西着火了，火势不严重，已经熄灭了，他们正在抢修。别担心，没有危险。",
      "next": "n73"
    },
    {
      "id": "n73",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_stopped_day.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "她做了个不太淑女的手势，仿佛想把危险事故丢到一边，把那当作无关紧要的事。",
      "next": "n74"
    },
    {
      "id": "n74",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window_day.png",
      "speaker": "debenham",
      "text": "是的，是的，我明白，可是，时间！",
      "next": "n75"
    },
    {
      "id": "n75",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window_day.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "时间？",
      "next": "n76"
    },
    {
      "id": "n76",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window_day.png",
      "speaker": "debenham",
      "text": "没错，会延误的。",
      "next": "n77"
    },
    {
      "id": "n77",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window_day.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "有可能——没错。",
      "next": "n78"
    },
    {
      "id": "n78",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window_day.png",
      "speaker": "debenham",
      "text": "可我们不能误点！火车应该在六点五十五分到达，可我还得穿过博斯普鲁斯海峡，到对岸去坐九点钟的辛普朗东方快车，如果晚一两个小时，就赶不上那趟列车了！",
      "next": "n79"
    },
    {
      "id": "n79",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window_day.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "有可能——没错。",
      "next": "n80"
    },
    {
      "id": "n80",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window_day.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "他好奇地看着她。她握着窗口栏杆的那只手有些不稳，嘴唇也在哆嗦着。",
      "next": "n81"
    },
    {
      "id": "n81",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window_day.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "这对你很重要吗，小姐？",
      "next": "n82"
    },
    {
      "id": "n82",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window_day.png",
      "speaker": "debenham",
      "text": "（声音紧张）嗯嗯，很重要。我——我必须赶上那趟车。",
      "next": "n83"
    },
    {
      "id": "n83",
      "type": "choice",
      "bg": "train_window_day.png",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "c1",
          "text": "安慰她",
          "next": "segment_meet_bouc_start"
        },
        {
          "id": "c2",
          "text": "询问焦虑的具体原因",
          "next": "segment_meet_bouc_start"
        },
        {
          "id": "c3",
          "text": "只是观察不做反应",
          "next": "segment_meet_bouc_start"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "segment_meet_bouc_start",
      "type": "segment",
      "title": "与布克相遇",
      "next": "n84"
    },
    {
      "id": "n84",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window_day.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "她从他身边走开，去过道找阿巴思诺特上校了。",
      "next": "n85"
    },
    {
      "id": "n85",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_moving_day.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "然而她完全没有必要担忧。十分钟之后火车又开动了。到海德帕萨时只晚了五分钟，损失的时间在途中补了回来。",
      "next": "n86"
    },
    {
      "id": "n86",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_moving_day.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "博斯普鲁斯海峡风高浪急，波洛先生很不舒服，他在船上和同行的旅伴分开了，没有再见到他们。",
      "next": "n87"
    },
    {
      "id": "n87",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lobby.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "波洛抵达斯坦布尔，入住托卡林旅馆。",
      "next": "n88"
    },
    {
      "id": "n88",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lobby.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "（走向门房）有没有我的信件？",
      "next": "n89"
    },
    {
      "id": "n89",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lobby.png",
      "speaker": "porter",
      "text": "有三封信和一封电报，先生。",
      "next": "n90"
    },
    {
      "id": "n90",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lobby.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "（打开电报，皱眉）你预测的卡斯纳案件有了突破进展，请速回。",
      "next": "n91"
    },
    {
      "id": "n91",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lobby.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "（对门房）烦人。我今晚就得走。辛普朗东方快车什么时候开？",
      "next": "n92"
    },
    {
      "id": "n92",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lobby.png",
      "speaker": "porter",
      "text": "九点，先生。每年这个时候都不难买票。",
      "next": "n93"
    },
    {
      "id": "n93",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_restaurant.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "波洛在餐厅用餐，观察其他客人。",
      "next": "n94"
    },
    {
      "id": "n94",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_restaurant.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "（把手搭在波洛肩上）啊，老朋友，这真是个意外的惊喜！",
      "next": "n95"
    },
    {
      "id": "n95",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_restaurant.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "布克先生！",
      "next": "n96"
    },
    {
      "id": "n96",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_restaurant.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "这次算是离家远行了吧，亲爱的？",
      "next": "n97"
    },
    {
      "id": "n97",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_restaurant.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "在叙利亚有点小事。",
      "next": "n98"
    },
    {
      "id": "n98",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_restaurant.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "啊，所以你是要回家了？什么时候？",
      "next": "n99"
    },
    {
      "id": "n99",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_restaurant.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "今晚。我刚刚让他们买了一张卧铺票，本来打算在这儿待几天。可我又接到一封电报，说有重要的事要我回英国。",
      "next": "n100"
    },
    {
      "id": "n100",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_restaurant.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "波洛注意到餐厅另一桌的两个美国人。",
      "next": "n101"
    },
    {
      "id": "n101",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_restaurant.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "（心想）年轻的那位三十岁上下，长相讨喜。年长的那个……从远处看，俨然一副慈善家的和善面孔，但那双小眼睛露了馅儿——眼窝深陷，眼神十分狡诈。",
      "next": "n102"
    },
    {
      "id": "n102",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_restaurant.png",
      "speaker": "rachett",
      "text": "（声音沙哑柔软）结账去，赫克托。",
      "next": "n103"
    },
    {
      "id": "n103",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_restaurant.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "老人从波洛身边经过时，波洛感到一种奇怪的感觉——好像是一只野兽，一只凶残的野兽，从他身边窜了过去。",
      "next": "n104"
    },
    {
      "id": "n104",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_restaurant.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "完成这个艰巨的任务之后，波洛环视四周，等着他的下一道菜。餐厅里只有六个人，其中两个人引起了赫尔克里·波洛的注意。",
      "next": "n105"
    },
    {
      "id": "n105",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_restaurant.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "这两个人坐在离他不远的桌子旁，年轻一点儿的三十岁上下，长相讨喜，明显是个美国人。然而让这个小个子侦探感兴趣的却是他的同伴。",
      "next": "n106"
    },
    {
      "id": "n106",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_restaurant.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "（仔细观察）这个男人有六七十岁，从远处看，俨然一副慈善家的和善面孔，有点秃顶，圆圆的额头，微笑起来露出一排洁白的假牙——这些都展示了他随和的性格。只是那双小眼睛露了馅儿——眼窝深陷，眼神十分狡诈。",
      "next": "n107"
    },
    {
      "id": "n107",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_restaurant.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "还不止这些。他跟他年轻的同伴说话时，扫了一眼房间，瞪了波洛片刻，就在这一瞬间，脸上流露出一种奇怪的恶毒神情，透着不自然的紧张。",
      "next": "n108"
    },
    {
      "id": "n108",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lobby.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "随后，雷切特站起身。",
      "next": "n109"
    },
    {
      "id": "n109",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lobby.png",
      "speaker": "rachett",
      "text": "（声音沙哑柔软）结账去，赫克托。",
      "next": "n110"
    },
    {
      "id": "n110",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lobby.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "他的声音有些沙哑，柔软中含有古怪和危险的意味。",
      "next": "n111"
    },
    {
      "id": "n111",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lobby.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "波洛在休息室遇见他的朋友时，之前那两个人正准备离开旅馆。他们的行李被送到了楼下，年轻的那位在打理这些事，没多久，他打开玻璃门，说道：",
      "next": "n112"
    },
    {
      "id": "n112",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lobby.png",
      "speaker": "mcdonald",
      "text": "都准备妥当了，雷切特先生。",
      "next": "n113"
    },
    {
      "id": "n113",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lobby.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "那老人咕哝了一声表示知道了，接着便走了出去。",
      "next": "n114"
    },
    {
      "id": "n114",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lounge.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "那么，你怎么看这两个人？",
      "next": "n115"
    },
    {
      "id": "n115",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lounge.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "他们是美国人。",
      "next": "n116"
    },
    {
      "id": "n116",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lounge.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "的确是美国人。我是说，对他们的性格你怎么看？",
      "next": "n117"
    },
    {
      "id": "n117",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lounge.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "那个年轻人挺有礼貌的。",
      "next": "n118"
    },
    {
      "id": "n118",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lounge.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "另一个呢？",
      "next": "n119"
    },
    {
      "id": "n119",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lounge.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "实话说，我的朋友，我没怎么留意他。他给我的印象不太好。你觉得呢？",
      "next": "n120"
    },
    {
      "id": "n120",
      "type": "choice",
      "bg": "hotel_lounge.png",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "c1",
          "text": "详细描述野兽般的直觉",
          "next": "segment_housing_argument_start"
        },
        {
          "id": "c2",
          "text": "简单说印象不好",
          "next": "segment_housing_argument_start"
        },
        {
          "id": "c3",
          "text": "暂时保留看法",
          "next": "segment_housing_argument_start"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "segment_housing_argument_start",
      "type": "segment",
      "title": "住房争吵",
      "next": "n121"
    },
    {
      "id": "n121",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lounge.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "（停顿了一会儿）在餐厅他从我身边经过时，我有种奇怪的感觉。就好像是一只野兽，一只凶残的野兽，从我身边窜了过去。凶残的，你明白吗？",
      "next": "n122"
    },
    {
      "id": "n122",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lounge.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "可他看起来是一副受人尊敬的样子。",
      "next": "n123"
    },
    {
      "id": "n123",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lounge.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "没错！他的身体——那笼子——怎么看都那么令人尊敬，可是透过栏杆，那只野兽却在盯着你。",
      "next": "n124"
    },
    {
      "id": "n124",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lounge.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "你的想象力真丰富，我的朋友。",
      "next": "n125"
    },
    {
      "id": "n125",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lounge.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "也许是吧，可我怎么也摆脱不了邪恶跟我擦肩而过的感觉。",
      "next": "n126"
    },
    {
      "id": "n126",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lounge.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "那位可敬的美国绅士吗？",
      "next": "n127"
    },
    {
      "id": "n127",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lounge.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "就是那位可敬的美国绅士。",
      "next": "n128"
    },
    {
      "id": "n128",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lounge.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "好啦，可能你说得对。这世界上的邪恶太多了。",
      "next": "n129"
    },
    {
      "id": "n129",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lobby.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "就在这时，门开了，门房朝他们走来，一脸忧虑和抱歉。",
      "next": "n130"
    },
    {
      "id": "n130",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lobby.png",
      "speaker": "porter",
      "text": "太不寻常了，先生，火车上没有头等厢卧铺票了。",
      "next": "n131"
    },
    {
      "id": "n131",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lobby.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "（喊出了声）什么？这时候？肯定是旅游团，还是政客出访什么的——",
      "next": "n132"
    },
    {
      "id": "n132",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lobby.png",
      "speaker": "porter",
      "text": "我不清楚，先生，可的确是这样。",
      "next": "n133"
    },
    {
      "id": "n133",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lobby.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "好吧，好吧，别担心，我的朋友，我们会安排好的。十六号卧铺房总是空的，那是列车员说了算的！",
      "next": "n134"
    },
    {
      "id": "n134",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "hotel_lobby.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "（看了一眼挂钟）走吧，我们出发。",
      "next": "n135"
    },
    {
      "id": "n135",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "晚上九点，火车站。布克先生和波洛准备登上辛普朗东方快车。",
      "next": "n136"
    },
    {
      "id": "n136",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": "conductor",
      "text": "晚上好，先生。您在一号房间。",
      "next": "n137"
    },
    {
      "id": "n137",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "我听说今天的卧铺都满了？",
      "next": "n138"
    },
    {
      "id": "n138",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": "conductor",
      "text": "太不可思议了，先生，全世界的人都选择在今晚出行！",
      "next": "n139"
    },
    {
      "id": "n139",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "不管怎样你都得帮这位先生找一间卧铺房，他是我的朋友，他可以住在十六号房。",
      "next": "n140"
    },
    {
      "id": "n140",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": "conductor",
      "text": "已经有人了，先生。",
      "next": "n141"
    },
    {
      "id": "n141",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "什么？十六号？",
      "next": "n142"
    },
    {
      "id": "n142",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "他们心照不宣地交换了个眼神，列车员笑了。他是个脸色发黄的高个子中年人。",
      "next": "n143"
    },
    {
      "id": "n143",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": "conductor",
      "text": "是的，先生，就像我跟您说的那样，车里已经满满的了——到处都是人。",
      "next": "n144"
    },
    {
      "id": "n144",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "（气呼呼地质问）怎么回事？是什么地方开会吗？还是旅游团？",
      "next": "n145"
    },
    {
      "id": "n145",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": "conductor",
      "text": "不是的，先生，这纯属巧合。刚好很多人都选择了今晚搭这趟火车。",
      "next": "n146"
    },
    {
      "id": "n146",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "布克先生生气地感叹了几声。",
      "next": "n147"
    },
    {
      "id": "n147",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "在贝尔格莱德，会加一节从雅典开过来的车厢，还有一节布加勒斯特到巴黎的车厢。可我们明天晚上才能到贝尔格莱德，今晚是个问题。二等卧铺也没有空位了吗？",
      "next": "n148"
    },
    {
      "id": "n148",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": "conductor",
      "text": "二等卧铺有一个，先生——",
      "next": "n149"
    },
    {
      "id": "n149",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "好，那就——",
      "next": "n150"
    },
    {
      "id": "n150",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": "conductor",
      "text": "但那是个女士卧铺，而且已经有一位德国女士在里面了——一个女仆。",
      "next": "n151"
    },
    {
      "id": "n151",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "哎呀，真不巧。",
      "next": "n152"
    },
    {
      "id": "n152",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "别烦恼了，我的朋友，我坐普通车厢就行。",
      "next": "n153"
    },
    {
      "id": "n153",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "不行，不行。旅客都到齐了吗？",
      "next": "n154"
    },
    {
      "id": "n154",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": "conductor",
      "text": "（面带迟疑）其实，还有一位旅客没到。",
      "next": "n155"
    },
    {
      "id": "n155",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "说下去！",
      "next": "n156"
    },
    {
      "id": "n156",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": "conductor",
      "text": "二等卧铺的七号房。现在差四分钟九点，这位先生还没来。",
      "next": "n157"
    },
    {
      "id": "n157",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "是谁？",
      "next": "n158"
    },
    {
      "id": "n158",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": "conductor",
      "text": "（查了查名单）一个英国人，姓哈里斯。",
      "next": "n159"
    },
    {
      "id": "n159",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "这名字是个好兆头，根据我的狄更斯小说，这位哈里斯先生不会来了。",
      "next": "n160"
    },
    {
      "id": "n160",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "把这位先生的行李搬到七号房间。如果哈里斯先生来了，就跟他说已经晚了，卧铺不能为他留太久，到时我们再设法另行安排。我干吗要在乎这位哈里斯先生呢？",
      "next": "n161"
    },
    {
      "id": "n161",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": "conductor",
      "text": "全听您的吩咐。",
      "next": "n162"
    },
    {
      "id": "n162",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_corridor.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "列车员给波洛的搬运工指了路，自己则闪到车厢踏板的一边，请波洛上火车。",
      "next": "n163"
    },
    {
      "id": "n163",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_corridor.png",
      "speaker": "conductor",
      "text": "最里面倒数第二间，先生。",
      "next": "n164"
    },
    {
      "id": "n164",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_corridor.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "波洛缓缓地沿着过道走过去，大部分旅客在自己房间外面站着。他像钟表那样有规律且礼貌地说着'对不起'，最后终于走到了指定的房间，里面有人正伸手拿行李，正是在托卡林旅馆见到的那个年轻的高个子的美国人。",
      "next": "n165"
    },
    {
      "id": "n165",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_corridor.png",
      "speaker": "mcdonald",
      "text": "（皱了皱眉）对不起，我想你弄错了。",
      "next": "n166"
    },
    {
      "id": "n166",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_corridor.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "接着又用法语费力地重复了一遍。",
      "next": "n167"
    },
    {
      "id": "n167",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_corridor.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "（用英语回答）你是哈里斯先生吗？",
      "next": "n168"
    },
    {
      "id": "n168",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_corridor.png",
      "speaker": "mcdonald",
      "text": "不，我叫麦奎因。我——",
      "next": "n169"
    },
    {
      "id": "n169",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_corridor.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "但就在这时，列车员的声音从波洛肩头传了过来——带有歉意而且急促的声音。",
      "next": "n170"
    },
    {
      "id": "n170",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_corridor.png",
      "speaker": "conductor",
      "text": "火车上没有别的卧铺了，先生，这位先生只能住在这儿了。",
      "next": "n171"
    },
    {
      "id": "n171",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_compartment.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "说这话时，他拉起了过道上的窗户，把波洛的行李拎了进来。波洛对列车员语气中的歉意饶有兴致。这人肯定答应给列车员一笔不菲的小费，好让自己不受其他旅客的打扰，独自享用这个房间。可是，再慷慨的小费也不顶用了，因为公司的董事上了火车并下达了命令。",
      "next": "n172"
    },
    {
      "id": "n172",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_compartment.png",
      "speaker": "conductor",
      "text": "都放好了，先生。您住上铺，七号房，火车一分钟后就开动了。",
      "next": "n173"
    },
    {
      "id": "n173",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_compartment.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "说完，他便沿着过道匆匆走开。波洛走进房间。",
      "next": "n174"
    },
    {
      "id": "n174",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_compartment.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "（愉快地说）我可从没见过列车员亲自摆放行李，真是闻所未闻！",
      "next": "n175"
    },
    {
      "id": "n175",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_compartment.png",
      "speaker": "mcdonald",
      "text": "（笑了笑）这列火车真是座无虚席啊！",
      "next": "n176"
    },
    {
      "id": "n176",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_compartment.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "显然他已经忘记了刚才的不快——也许他觉得再追究此事也没什么意义了。",
      "next": "n177"
    },
    {
      "id": "n177",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window_departing.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "随着汽笛一声巨响，火车头也凄凉地长啸一声。两人都从房间来到过道上，外面有个声音大喊：'上车！'",
      "next": "n178"
    },
    {
      "id": "n178",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window_departing.png",
      "speaker": "mcdonald",
      "text": "车开了。",
      "next": "n179"
    },
    {
      "id": "n179",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window_departing.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "但火车并没有开动，又传来一声汽笛。",
      "next": "n180"
    },
    {
      "id": "n180",
      "type": "choice",
      "bg": "train_window_departing.png",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "c1",
          "text": "接受好意，睡下铺",
          "next": "segment_train_start_start"
        },
        {
          "id": "c2",
          "text": "婉言谢绝，坚持睡上铺",
          "next": "segment_train_start_start"
        },
        {
          "id": "c3",
          "text": "提议轮流睡下铺",
          "next": "segment_train_start_start"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "segment_train_start_start",
      "type": "segment",
      "title": "火车启动",
      "next": "n181"
    },
    {
      "id": "n181",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window_departing.png",
      "speaker": "mcdonald",
      "text": "我说，先生，如果你愿意睡下铺——如果方便的话——别客气，我都行。",
      "next": "n182"
    },
    {
      "id": "n182",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window_departing.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "真是个可爱的小伙子。",
      "next": "n183"
    },
    {
      "id": "n183",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window_departing.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "不，不，我不能——",
      "next": "n184"
    },
    {
      "id": "n184",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window_departing.png",
      "speaker": "mcdonald",
      "text": "没关系——",
      "next": "n185"
    },
    {
      "id": "n185",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window_departing.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "你太客气了——",
      "next": "n186"
    },
    {
      "id": "n186",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window_departing.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "两人谦让着。",
      "next": "n187"
    },
    {
      "id": "n187",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window_departing.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "只是一个晚上，到贝尔格莱德——",
      "next": "n188"
    },
    {
      "id": "n188",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window_departing.png",
      "speaker": "mcdonald",
      "text": "哦，我明白了。你在贝尔格莱德下车——",
      "next": "n189"
    },
    {
      "id": "n189",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window_departing.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "也不全是。你知道——",
      "next": "n190"
    },
    {
      "id": "n190",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window_moving.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "火车猛然一动，两人被晃到窗口，看到灯火通明的站台缓缓地从他们身边远去。",
      "next": "n191"
    },
    {
      "id": "n191",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_window_moving.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "东方快车开始了为期三天的贯穿欧洲之旅。",
      "next": "segment_refuse_case_start"
    },
    {
      "id": "segment_refuse_case_start",
      "type": "segment",
      "title": "拒绝接受案子",
      "next": "n192"
    },
    {
      "id": "n192",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "第二天，波洛稍晚了一些才去餐车吃午饭。他起得很早，一个人吃了早饭，整个上午都在阅读那些让他回伦敦办案的文件，没怎么见过他的旅伴。",
      "next": "n193"
    },
    {
      "id": "n193",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "布克先生已经坐在了桌边，招呼波洛坐在对面的空位上。波洛坐了下来，马上发现自己正坐在最佳的位置上——头一个享受餐点，而且种类丰富，味道出奇的好。",
      "next": "n194"
    },
    {
      "id": "n194",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "如果我有巴尔扎克的文笔，就能好好描述一下这番景象了。我们周围的人，不同的阶层、不同的国籍、不同的年龄段，三天的旅程把这些互不相识的人聚集在一起……",
      "next": "n195"
    },
    {
      "id": "n195",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "除非发生什么事故……那么，这儿的所有人没准就被死亡联系在一起了。",
      "next": "n196"
    },
    {
      "id": "n196",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "你太吓人了，我的朋友！也许是消化不良了。",
      "next": "n197"
    },
    {
      "id": "n197",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "波洛观察餐车里的旅客：意大利商人、英国男仆、美国推销员、俄国德拉戈米罗夫公主、瑞典太太、玛丽·德贝纳姆、阿巴思诺特上校、德国女仆、匈牙利情侣、麦奎因和雷切特。",
      "next": "n198"
    },
    {
      "id": "n198",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "午餐后，雷切特出乎意料地坐在了波洛对面。",
      "next": "n199"
    },
    {
      "id": "n199",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car.png",
      "speaker": "rachett",
      "text": "能借个火吗？我姓雷切特。我想我有幸跟赫赫有名的赫尔克里·波洛先生说话，对吗？",
      "next": "n200"
    },
    {
      "id": "n200",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "您所知正确，先生。",
      "next": "n201"
    },
    {
      "id": "n201",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car.png",
      "speaker": "rachett",
      "text": "在我们国家，人们说话一向开门见山。波洛先生，我希望你能接受我的一个委托。这可是一大笔钱。",
      "next": "n202"
    },
    {
      "id": "n202",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "先生，如今我的顾客十分有限，我很少接案子了。",
      "next": "n203"
    },
    {
      "id": "n203",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car.png",
      "speaker": "rachett",
      "text": "波洛先生，我是个有钱人，非常有钱。高处不胜寒啊。我有个敌人。我的生命受到了威胁。",
      "next": "n204"
    },
    {
      "id": "n204",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "只有一个敌人吗？",
      "next": "n205"
    },
    {
      "id": "n205",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car.png",
      "speaker": "rachett",
      "text": "你这话是什么意思？",
      "next": "n206"
    },
    {
      "id": "n206",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "先生，以我的经验来看，如果一个人到了你说的那个地位，往往不止有一个敌人。",
      "next": "n207"
    },
    {
      "id": "n207",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car.png",
      "speaker": "rachett",
      "text": "（掏出手枪）我认为自己还不至于遭人暗算，但我要保证自己的安全万无一失。请记住，这可是一大笔钱。",
      "next": "n208"
    },
    {
      "id": "n208",
      "type": "choice",
      "bg": "train_dining_car.png",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "c1",
          "text": "接受委托，保护雷切特",
          "next": "n209"
        },
        {
          "id": "c2",
          "text": "拒绝委托，离开餐车",
          "next": "n209"
        },
        {
          "id": "c3",
          "text": "要求更多信息再做决定",
          "next": "n209"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "n209",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car.png",
      "speaker": "rachett",
      "text": "两万美元能打动你吗？",
      "next": "n210"
    },
    {
      "id": "n210",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "不能。",
      "next": "n211"
    },
    {
      "id": "n211",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car.png",
      "speaker": "rachett",
      "text": "如果你还想多要，那可不成，我是个识货的人。",
      "next": "n212"
    },
    {
      "id": "n212",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "我也是，雷切特先生。",
      "next": "n213"
    },
    {
      "id": "n213",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car.png",
      "speaker": "poirot",
      "text": "（站起身）容我说句不客气的话——我不喜欢你那张脸，雷切特先生。",
      "next": "n214"
    },
    {
      "id": "n214",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_dining_car.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "波洛离开了餐车。雷切特看着他离开，脸上露出阴郁的表情。",
      "next": "n215"
    },
    {
      "id": "n215",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "当晚，火车抵达贝尔格莱德。由于大雪，火车加挂了车厢。布克先生搬到雅典车厢，波洛则搬到斯坦布尔－加来车厢的一号房。",
      "next": "n216"
    },
    {
      "id": "n216",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": "bouc",
      "text": "但愿我们不会被大雪堵在路上，我跟你说，我可受不了！",
      "next": "n217"
    },
    {
      "id": "n217",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "bg": "train_station_night.png",
      "speaker": null,
      "text": "九点十五分，火车准时驶出车站，驶入风雪交加的夜晚。"
    }
  ]
}